You need to be attentive to the gas station next to the road, because right there you have to change the car, although in the vast majority of cases it will suffice what you have.
Cars are divided into three categories.
Sports are suitable for urban areas, American strong cars for straight highways and super-deportive exotics for technical driving, for example, by mountain roads with curves.
In addition, the main narrative thread also appears a thread of parallel challenges, that is, there are races in specific places that you will know for the stories.
Here you will get not only medals, but also points of experience for your profile, which serves both the challenges and the stories.
By reaching the top level, the driver opens up several possibilities, starting from the car and ending up with funds for the profile.
At the same time, there is connected an Autolog function online, which compares your results with those of other players and provides other community functions.
One of the most difficult elements to understand is how the last race in history is made.
With the car you get to the subway tunnel (pass), where you get to run dark through the tracks (pass).
The speed meter marks you between 150 and 200 km/h (pass) and, suddenly, behind you comes the subway convoy and takes you forward without further.
In the writing we will surely have a discussion about this for several days, about whether during the programming of the game no one even thought a little or if the authors really take us for a bunch of fools.
