"Going to Costa Rica is a dream come true"
In an exclusive interview with Viva, bassist Jeff Ament of Pearl Jam, said the band is ready to offer one of its best concerts next Sunday at the National Stadium.
It has been more than 20 years waiting, but the band ensures that for them it will also turn the dream of playing in the country into reality.
