The invaders had taken 11 of the 13 floors of the building, in Balmes, 51
The 12 occupants left the farm yesterday at noon without offering resistance
Everything seems to indicate that the nightmare that the neighbors of the 51st of Balmes Street has come to an end.
Twelve people voluntarily left yesterday's noon the building they were occupying illegally, where they organized macro-fests that were desperate to the neighborhood, in judicial order and without the need for police intervention.
